# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  GONUBIE HOUSE SITTING — Backend Environment Variables
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in every value before running.
#  NEVER commit .env to Git — it is listed in .gitignore.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Node environment ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Use "production" on Render, "development" locally
NODE_ENV=development

# ── Server ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=5000

# ── MongoDB Atlas ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Create a free cluster at https://cloud.mongodb.com
# 2. Click "Connect" → "Drivers" → copy the connection string
# 3. Replace <username>, <password>, and <dbname>
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/housesitting?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# ── Gmail SMTP (Nodemailer) ───────────────────────────────────
# Use your BUSINESS Gmail account (e.g. gonubiehousesit@gmail.com)
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT use your real Gmail password here.
# Instead, generate an App Password:
#   Google Account → Security → 2-Step Verification → App Passwords
#   Select "Mail" + "Other (custom name)" → Generate
#   Paste the 16-character code (no spaces) below.
GMAIL_USER=yourgmail@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ── Notification recipients ───────────────────────────────────
# Both email addresses will receive every booking, contact & meet-greet notification.
OWNER_EMAIL_1=yourname@email.com
OWNER_EMAIL_2=layla@email.com

# ── CORS — Frontend URL ───────────────────────────────────────
# Local development:
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
# Production (set this on Render to your Vercel domain):
# FRONTEND_URL=https://your-site.vercel.app
